mirage.mirage_boss_des_101:
Northern Duke—Björn is a nimble Warrior with the ability to create <color=@000082>clones</color>. His clones move around actively and help him by <color=@000082>sharing damage</color> taken.

Recommended Synergy(ies):
<color=@000082>Mystifiers</color>
mirage.mirage_boss_des_201:
King of Thorns—Merlin is a powerful <color=@000082>solo</color> Mage who possesses astounding <color=@000082>control abilities</color>.

Recommended Synergy(ies):
<color=@000082>Glorians</color>.
mirage.mirage_boss_des_301:
Ghost Bride—Emily has powerful <color=@000082>Curse abilities</color> and extremely strong Effect Resistance.

Recommended Synergy(ies):
<color=@000082>Doomsdayers</color>
mirage.mirage_boss_des_401:
Bloodhell Queen—Arkdina's moths infest the battlefield like a plague and carry a terryfing <color=@000082>Revive</color> effect.

Recommended Synergy(ies):
<color=@000082>Valiantors</color>
mirage.mirage_boss_des_501:
Dungeon Maniac—Percival's tentacles deal a devastating <color=@000082>Instant Kill</color> effect on a single target.

Recommended Synergy(ies):
<color=@000082>Avengers</color>
mirage.mirage_feature_des_1:
Penalty: Applies <color=@000082>8 stacks of Corrode</color> to Björn or decreases his damage against heroes with <color=@000082>4 stacks of ATK</color> by <color=@000082>-90%</color>.

Recommended Synergy(ies): <color=@000082>Mystifiers</color>.
mirage.mirage_feature_des_2:
Penalty: After an ally unit is revived, they receive <color=@000082>ATK +400% and DMG RED +60%</color>. Divine and Demon heroes gain <color=@000082>CRIT DMG Boost +400%</color> when dealing PDMG.

Recommended Synergy(ies): <color=@000082>Avengers</color>
mirage.mirage_feature_des_3:
Penalty: The ally team receives <color=@000082>Reflect Rate +150%</color>. Divine and Demon heroes gain <color=@000082>CRIT DMG Boost +400%</color> when dealing PDMG.

Recommended Synergy(ies): <color=@000082>Doomsdayers<color=@000082>
mirage.mirage_feature_des_4:
Penalty: Gangenir's machines possess shields that can <color=@000082>share damage</color> taken.
Recommendation: Heroes with <color=@000082>strong AoE skills</color>.
mirage.mirage_feature_des_5:
Penalty: Heroes with <color=@000082>Assail</color> or <color=@000082>4 stacks of ATK</color> buffs take <color=@000082>-90%</color> damage from Arkdina.

Recommended Synergy(ies): <color=@000082>Valiantors</color>.
